We should add the orderBody?: boolean property in the RetrievalOptions interface, otherwise we can not sort in the body.

RetrievalOptions interface {
         fields?: string [];
         exprs?: AnyObject <string>;
         limit?: number;
         offset?: number;
         order?: OrderingOptions [];
         **orderBody?: boolean;**
         pageLength?: number;
     }

